BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:drndoCiGtwlB91KeRhi82
SUMMARY:Kaleidoscope Play & Learn / 万花筒游戏和学习@笔架山分店 / 萬花筒遊戲和學習@筆架山分店
DTSTAMP:20260314T154850Z
DTSTART:20260317T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Children listen to multilingual stories\, sing songs and do sim
	ple arts and crafts with their caregivers during the group time. There is 
	also a play time for children to explore various toys and play activities.
	Event is in English and Mandarin.-----------------------------------------
	------------------------------------------萬花筒邊玩邊學®: 孩子與他們的照顧者在小組中一起聽多種語言故事
	、唱歌並做簡單的手工。萬花筒邊玩邊學®也是一個提供孩子們探索各種玩具和遊戲活動的時間。本活動將以國語和英語進行。------------------
	-----------------------------------------------------------------万花筒边玩边学®:
	 孩子与他们的照顾者在小组中一起听多种语言故事、唱歌并做简单的手工。万花筒边玩边学®也是一个提供給孩子们探索各种玩具和游戏活动的时间。本次活动将以普
	通话和英语进行。\n\nhttps://www.spl.org/event-calendar?trumbaEmbed=view%3devent%26
	eventid%3d195963074
URL:https://www.spl.org/event-calendar?trumbaEmbed=view%3devent%26eventid%3
	d195963074
LOCATION:Beacon Hill Branch\, Meeting Room
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
